snippet.title: EverQuest: The Broken Mirror [Official Trailer]
snippet.description:
The Broken Mirror is now available! BUY NOW: http://bit.ly/EQ-Mirror

This expansion features instanced versions of Plane of Hate and Plane of Fear that scale for players ranging from level 75 through 105. 

Join us for The Broken Mirror, the 22nd EverQuest expansion, that has new zones, must-have in-game items, and adds the new Illusion Ring Key feature to the game!

Want to play EverQuest, the game that defined the MMORPG genre, for FREE? https://www.everquest.com/register
